peopleAlsoAsk.question: What is the best headshot for LinkedIn?
peopleAlsoAsk.title: Top Tips For Great LinkedIn Headshots
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: Correctly sized. Linkedin headshots are best sized in a square ratio, at 400x400 pixels. Make sure your head and shoulders take up most of the frame. You want to avoid having too much space, as well as being too close. A nice balance is the key.Jan 16, 2019
